{
  "stem": "26765.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And if there was any little piece of lint, any excuse, they would take the-- I guess, the leader of the barrack, and beat, beat the person.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was, that was terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we had to stand at roll call, [? at ?] [? appel, ?] every morning and-- for hours and hours.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And you know, well, at that time, it was still nice and-- fairly nice, springtime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it wasn't too cold or too hot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But still, we had to stand a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was a woman by the name of Flo Isaak who took me under her wing, and she kind of looked after me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so, I wasn't so alone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But as I was saying, on my eighth birthday we were called to the commandant's office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And you know, I thought we were going to get beaten or we had done something wrong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But when we got to the commandant's office, there was Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Van Mackelenbergh sitting in his office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I was just so overjoyed that I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And another officer, a very cruel officer, Epplinger, he took me and he put me on his lap.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And of course, I was scared to death, you know, to be sitting there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But on the other hand, I was also afraid to say, I don't want to sit here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But I had often seen him hitting people, Epplinger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Well, I forgot about Epplinger because Mr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Van Mackelenbergh was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he said, you know, he was there for my birthday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he brought package with food and chocolates.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And he said he was going to visit us again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And the reason-- this was highly unusual for any civilian to come into the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "What had happened was this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
